13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 2401, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 2401. Sections 4 2401 through 10 2407 of this act title
17 shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma State Regents'
18 Academic Rising Scholars Award Act.".
19 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 2402, is
20 amended to read as follows:
21 Section 2402. A. There is hereby created the Oklahoma State
22 Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award Program. The purpose of the
23 Oklahoma State Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award Program is to
24 retain top-ranked students from Oklahoma in Oklahoma colleges,
ENGR. H. B. NO. 1282 Page 1
1 enab le Oklahoma institutions of higher education to compete
2 aggressively for top Oklahoma scholars, attract high-caliber out-of-
3 state students to Oklahoma to attend colleges and universities, and
4 enhance the academic quality in Oklahoma colleges and universities.
5 The program shall provide participants funding for enrollment fees,
6 tuition and other fees, room and board and required textbooks or
7 materials for up to five (5) years of undergraduate and/or graduate
8 study at accredited institutions of higher education in Oklahoma.
9 B. The Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education shall
10 administer the provisions of the Oklahoma State Regents' Academic
11 Rising Scholars Award Program.
