18 shall mean a student nominated by an institution in
19 The Oklahoma State System of Higher Education:
20 (1) whose American College Testing Program or
21 Scholastic Aptitude Test score falls within the
22 95.0 to 99.49 percentile levels, or
23 (2) who shows exceptional academic achievement as
